                </div>

                <div className="bg-yellow-50 p-3 rounded-lg">
                  <p className="text-sm text-yellow-800">
                    <strong>Demo codes to try:</strong><br />
                    • HV_sample1_demo123<br />
                    • HV_sample2_demo456<br />
                    • Any patient's QR code from their dashboard
